    "summary": "On 19 November 2022 at approximately 0430 hours, motor vessel Jacob Gerald allided into WD 31 E platform structure while transporting personnel. The captain dozed off at the helm prior to impact. One production operator aboard sustained minor back soreness. Platform structural damage occurred to several support members but no pollution or safety system damage resulted. Platform remained operational under Safe Operations Plan pending repairs.",
